{"tid":1233741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢喺金鐘既人可以去禮賓府","createTime":"2019-06-16T21:00:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T16:30:53.000Z","uid":69285,"like":536,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":134,"replies":[{"pid":"9d7f7dff6215d9157952766c08dd08d00ce0cd6e","tid":1233741,"uid":69285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:00:01.000Z","msg":"隔離post見到有巴打留言，覺得可能係突圍既方法<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mCK2e0B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmCK2e0B.png&h=50f39584&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（唔識點quote唔好意思）<br />\n <br />\n1. 有明確目標<br />\n- 可以迫佢即時回應 要佢出嚟 佢無得一世唔出嚟 包保佢走唔到 亦都唔係格硬衝入去<br />\n<br />\n2. 有走佬路線<br />\n- 一面可以去高院去動植物園落翻金鐘 一面又可以過SOHO落長實落中環 <br />\n<br />\n3. 減少市民之間衝突<br />\n- 唔係主要幹道 唔會引起交通大擠塞 俾香港人知道我地係針對林奠<br />\n<br />\n咁多年夏愨道 龍和道都守夠 都知得個守字 佢地有晒對付佔中嘅攻略 我地一啲優勢都無 不如主動出擊 <br />\n起碼殺佢一個措手不及 佢地唔知點應對 <br />\n收錢搞事嗰啲都一下子亂哂<br />\n<br />\n利申 希望大家討論下 小弟一個腦袋可能諗得唔夠好 <br />\n好唔好都比下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如時間方面"},{"pid":"53c7e33f2d962a9d1dbfda083e8fae7df440c854","tid":1233741,"uid":69285,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:01:08.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce8bdff24a21f4cdd61467096756ca0637e1c67","tid":1233741,"uid":69285,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:01:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b959e4ca08188be6f317f80b7fa84564d8596d6","tid":1233741,"uid":209620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:03:04.000Z","msg":"真心有疑問<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233720\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233720</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68fa643d404fdae710162fb2f2ef1b6c1ab4f8d7","tid":1233741,"uid":176840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T21:04:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96920e29fbc759200a02ad35d287ca